text: This is Clark Spring Lake on Anna Maria Island. The lake used to be crystal clear until a sewage spill back in 2015. Home owners are still frustrated with the situation, 3 years later. Reporter Rick Adams will be live tonight at 6pm with details. @mysuncoast https://t.co/UUBQ8NyvEL
